# Standards bootstrap

Before making changes in this repository:

1. Follow `.cursor/rules/collaboration.mdc` (review with user before git; ask when unclear).
2. Follow `.cursor/rules/meeting-notes-workflow.mdc` (summary format and living-doc updates).
3. Read `.cursor/skills/meeting-transcript-processor/SKILL.md` when processing a transcript or
   updating `project-management/meeting-summaries/`, `OPEN_QUESTIONS.md`, or `POC_NEXT_STEPS.md`.

These standards are mandatory for all sessions in this repository.
